    "1760211615cfa0f8d7": {
      "type": "_blocks",
      "blocks": {
        "ai_gen_block_46f1420_hrgNFM": {
          "type": "ai_gen_block_46f1420",
          "name": "About me",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Fashion Positions Installation",
            "description": "<p>Now in its seventh season, Fashion Positions features the debut of Marie-Louise Müller, who collaborates with the established designer <a href=\"https:\/\/utefaber.de\/\">Ute Faber<\/a> in an installation that unites fashion, craft, and sculptural design. At its center lies a hand-embroidered and painted tablecloth, transforming the table into a surface of visual storytelling.<\/p><p>Two design pieces from the <em>TABLE TALES<\/em> collection are presented: a flowing silk dress in vivid orange and a fully crocheted green dress shaped through intricate textures. They are accompanied by Faber’s characteristic, iconic shoe sculptures, which extend the dialogue between garment and object.<\/p><p>The installation highlights garments as objects of expression, bridging the worlds of fashion and art while inviting viewers into a shared narrative space.<\/p>",
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/fashionpositions01.png",
            "button_text": "Learn more",
            "button_link": "",
